Program: Discovery
Title: The communications revolution
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrz73
Last Broadcast Date: 15 August 2006
A look at the evolution of the radio. How modern infrastructure and the world wide web have brought us all closer together. It's a long way from Marconi's first Atlantic wireless transmission in December 1901. The programme looks at how mathematicians have been behind the breakthroughs made in 20th and 21st Century communications. Show less